However, the GTVA does not recognize this glory and BETAC prevents us from having authority in this sector.  Therefore, to make our voices heard, we will renounce the treaty and we will claim our territory by force."

3569, "(fr)Coup at Polaris

With the GTD Vindicator and the GTCv Belisarius secretly joining our ranks in the recent weeks, we are ready to formally declare our independence.  The time to throw down our disguises is upon us.

Our first thrust into the GTVA will be the new capital of the NTF, the Polaris system."

3570, "(fr)NTF offensive

With 93% of the 6th fleet poised to join our ranks and a small fleet of other rogue vessels pledging their loyalties to my cause, I am ready to unveil the tactics to take over the nearby systems.

In five hours at 0600 standard Earth time, The GTD Julius commanded by Admiral Edith will lead a fleet of nine warships and 32 squadrons of fighters.  The fleet will annex the Installation orbiting Polaris 3."

3571, "(fr)Ground assault

