3572, "(fr)Aftermath

With the Polaris system under NTF control, I will lead the rest of the fleet on a two pronged strike of of the Sirius and Deneb system, thereby solidifying the NTF's power in this sector.

Once these three systems and their respective jump nodes are secure, we will be in an adequate position to take on the GTVA forces."

