3856, "(fr)As you have been informed, we are preparing to mount an assault on a nearby $h NTF base of operations. The $f Voyager and the $f 347th will lead this attack. We have already taken up position in Polaris, and are preparing to jump to the location of the base.

Note that there are no Vasudans involved in this assault. Command has made this decision because the relations between us and them are strained enough right now, thanks again to the NTF. We are hoping that this operation will go a long way to resolving this."

