3860, "(fr)Once it has been eliminated, target the fighters and bombers. Protect the $f Voyager while it assaults the $h Lexington."

3861, "(fr)There are also ten $h cargo $h containers in the battlefield area. Scan them if you can, but destroying them is your next priority."

