3865, "(fr)Excellent job destroying all the NTF hostiles, pilots. Thanks to your perseverance, we have dealt the rebels a punishing blow. Their forces in this sector have been decimated by this attack, and I'm sure that will be reflected in any future attacks they may stage. Nice job."

3866, "(fr)Well, you managed to destroy all the NTF with the exception of the Ketracel. Fortunately, Iota wing of the 43rd 'Da Bomb' squad caught up with that straggler after it exited subspace. It was eliminated. We can't afford to leave behind survivors on raids like this one, pilots. Next time, it could cost us a lot more."

3867, "(fr)The Ketracel starts the mission en route to the node, so it has to die quickly. However, Beta Wing are already on the case. Just let them do their job, and there shouldn't be a problem."

3868, "(fr)In addition to this excellent performance, you managed to save the GTD Voyager. Considering the overwhelming odds you faced out there, this was a major achievement. The more destroyers we have, the better our chance to resist future incursions into our territory. Well done."

3869, "(fr)However, even in light of this, the GTD Voyager was destroyed. I suppose you could say that the crew's lives were not sacrificed in vain - after all, we did manage to take down a major NTF base of operations. Try explaining that to ten thousand grieving families."

3870, "(fr)The biggest threat to the Voyager are NTF bombers. Take them down before they enter range, and shoot down their warheads if thet get a chance to fire. After they are down, concentrate on other threats."

3871, "(fr)Saving the GTCv December showed that you are truly one of the GTVA elite. The corvette was equipped with only a skeleton crew, able to evacuate at a moment's notice, but you were able to save them. We never expected to have this ship back, yet we do. Great work."

3872, "(fr)Even though the Voyager was lost, the December survived. Not really comparable in number of lives saved, but at least we managed to show the NTF who is superior here."

3873, "(fr)The GTCv December was, unfortunately, destroyed. In light of all your other success this mission, this loss was minor. However, even the most minor loss of life is still a blow to the GTVA."

3874, "(fr)By the time the December enters, most of the sentries should be gone. Try taking down bombers before they can fire on the corvette."

3875, "(fr)The GTCv December was destroyed. This failure, combined with the loss of the GTD Voyager, is unacceptable! You are hereby grounded until further notice. A formal reprimand will be entered onto your record. We expected more from you, pilot."

